# Project Architecture

This is a full-stack Next.js application deployed on Cloudflare Workers with the following architecture:

## Tech Stack

- **Framework**: Next.js 15 (App Router) with React 19
- **Runtime**: Cloudflare Workers via OpenNext
- **Database**: Neon PostgreSQL with Drizzle ORM
- **Authentication**: Stack Auth (via @stackframe/stack)
- **AI Chat**: Assistant UI with Vercel AI SDK
- **State Management**: TanStack Query v5.90.3 (server state) + Zustand v5.0.8 (client state)
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS v4 + Shadcn UI (New York style)
- **Type Safety**: TypeScript with strict mode
- **Package Manager**: Bun 1.3

